if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('base_express')
and type = 'U')
drop table base_express
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: base_express */
/*==============================================================*/
create table base_express (
ExpressID int identity,
Name nvarchar(100) not null,
"Desc" nvarchar(3000) null,
AddTime datetime not null default getdate(),
IsDel bit not null default 0,
CountryID int null,
constraint PK_BASE_EXPRESS primary key (ExpressID)
)
go
